# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project-specific
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Generated simulation media — these are large and reproducible from code.
assets/generated/
*.mp4
*.gif

# Generated images under assets/generated/ are ignored; PNGs elsewhere
# (e.g. docs/, README screenshots checked in deliberately) are fine.
assets/generated/*.png

# Local notebooks / scratch
scratch/
*.ipynb

# Local adversarial critique — kept locally for context, not committed.
CRITIQUE.md

# Pipeline runtime artifacts (capability-scout, etc.) — gitignored
# because they're per-run and per-developer. The pipeline scaffold
# itself (.claude/agents, .claude/commands, .claude/scripts,
# .claude/references) IS committed.
.claude/notes/
.claude/agent-memory/
# Per-machine Claude Code state. ``settings.local.json`` holds the
# user's permission allow-list (different on every laptop) and
# ``worktrees/`` is the on-disk staging directory the harness uses
# for sub-agent worktrees (recursive copies of this repo — must not
# be committed).
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
